@startuml
actor User
participant Parser
participant TransactionsList
participant CurrencyConverter
participant Storage

== Step 1: Convert (view only) ==
User -> Parser : convert transaction 3 -to SGD
Parser -> TransactionsList : getTransactionById(3)
Parser -> CurrencyConverter : convert(...)
Parser -> User : display converted value
Parser -> Parser : store pending state

== Step 2: Confirm ==
User -> Parser : confirm
Parser -> TransactionsList : editTransaction(...)
TransactionsList -> Storage : save(...)
Storage --> TransactionsList : success
Parser -> User : "Transaction confirmed and stored"

@enduml
